{"data":{"id":"ChIJkUNPJRtfwokRdJ767vd2oJU","rating":5,"websiteUri":"https://kokahvac.com/","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":true,"periods":[{"open":{"day":0,"hour":0,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]},"userRatingCount":317,"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJkUNPJRtfwokRdJ767vd2oJU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBd1gwVkhUR2RDU1VodWVXcG5SVGRtVXpWMFgzYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 weeks ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Emilian and the technician that accompanied him during his job were very professional and sweet! We woke up to no hot water and no heat just a day before freezing temps and snow were forecasted. They repaired everything seamlessly and were very polite.\nWould definitely recommend their service to anyone and will be using them again!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Emilian and the technician that accompanied him during his job were very professional and sweet! We woke up to no hot water and no heat just a day before freezing temps and snow were forecasted. They repaired everything seamlessly and were very polite.\nWould definitely recommend their service to anyone and will be using them again!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Gracie Pyle","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100946547948220640317/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_GlbIHB9izIDhxlCwcsxWbk5Y3cA4Zjp3zaWJ9Gb-eks2LPI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-24T21:14:39.856325119Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBd1gwVkhUR2RDU1VodWVXcG5SVGRtVXpWMFgzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBd1gwVkhUR2RDU1VodWVXcG5SVGRtVXpWMFgzYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c25f1b254f4391:0x95a076f7eefa9e74"},{"name":"places/ChIJkUNPJRtfwokRdJ767vd2oJU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFM1EyRldYMTlOUVd4bU1ucEZURGRZVGt0V1RFRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"6 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"We had an excellent experience with Emilian and his team at Koka. They installed four mini split Daikin units for us and got all the work done in just one day. They also coordinated with an electrician, so we were fully up and running within three days total. The installation looks really clean— they even used a brown pipe covering that blends in nicely with our wall.  Everything looks very neat. The units are quiet and easy to use. We’re very thankful for their help and highly recommend them to anyone needing HVAC work!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"We had an excellent experience with Emilian and his team at Koka. They installed four mini split Daikin units for us and got all the work done in just one day. They also coordinated with an electrician, so we were fully up and running within three days total. The installation looks really clean— they even used a brown pipe covering that blends in nicely with our wall.  Everything looks very neat. The units are quiet and easy to use. We’re very thankful for their help and highly recommend them to anyone needing HVAC work!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Li Xiu Chen","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110719443328276480387/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg7JX1Dc21dfIVY0xcjNh13UZcjggR6F3H2HMAQ1Xf9WQJkIcB=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-08-19T11:47:02.977581089Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFM1EyRldYMTlOUVd4bU1ucEZURGRZVGt0V1RFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xFM1EyRldYMTlOUVd4bU1ucEZURGRZVGt0V1RFRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25f1b254f4391:0x95a076f7eefa9e74"},{"name":"places/ChIJkUNP